      <h1 class='title'>Employment Tribunal System Taskforce</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 14 November 2002 vol 394 cc1-2WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1ws' title='Col. 1WS &mdash; HC Deb 14 November 2002 vol 394 c1WS' name='column_1ws' href='#column_1ws' rel='bookmark'>1WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0394P0_20021114_CWS_2'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alan-johnson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0394P0_20021114_CWS_2' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alan Johnson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-alan-johnson" title="Mr Alan Johnson">The Minister for Employment Relations, Industry and the Regions (Alan Johnson)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">With my right honourable and noble Friend the Lord Chancellor I have today published the government's response to "Moving Forward: The Report of the Employment Tribunal System Taskforce".</p><p>I have placed copies in the Library of the House and it is also available on the DTI's Employment relations website <a class='resolved-url' href="http://www.dti.gov.uk/er">http://www.dti.gov.uk/er</a>.</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_2ws' title='Col. 2WS &mdash; HC Deb 14 November 2002 vol 394 c2WS' name='column_2ws' href='#column_2ws' rel='bookmark'>2WS</a>
        </blockquote>
